snippet.title: Interlocked Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Google Play and iTunes, try the unique 3D puzzle game Interlocked!

Know those puzzles consisting of a few wooden blocks that are impossible take apart? Then you know Interlocked. Each level, you’re given a unique and beautiful 3D puzzle consisting of blocks that hold each other together. Take it apart and you’ll feel ten times as smart.

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wecreatestuff.interlocked&hl=en
iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/interlocked/id554072547
